Module com.example.project3rubank
Package com.example.project3rubank.bank

Class Account

java.lang.Object
com.example.project3rubank.bank.Account
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Account>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Checking, Savings
public abstract class Account extends Object implements Comparable<Account>
The account class represents a bank account with an account number, account holder and an account balance. It provides methods for depositing, withdrawing and comparing accounts.
